data.description: 6 bedroom House in Osage Beach just minutes away from the lake, restaurants, grocery store and shopping. Come check out this over 4200 sq' home with a large 2 car garage at the end of a quite cul-de-sac, with in a quite neighborhood behind Dierbergs. Tennis courts, play ground and pool are just 1 block away down the rd off of Deer Run and Scout St. There is also a parking area for your boat trailers. You can enjoy one level living with 3 bedrooms, Kitchen, living room and laundry all on the main level. Lower level has 3 additional Bedrooms as well as a storage room and an office space or even more storage room. Large windows and sliding doors to upper deck and lower walk out porch to check out the view of the cove below. Lots of closets and storage throughout. Whether you have a large family or just enjoy hosting guest, you won't want to miss seeing this home. More pictures to come!
